Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.77,0:00:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.32,0:00:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你認為我太瘋狂也沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.33,0:00:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是能否答應我 陪我實現這樁事業
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.53,0:00:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪我的瘋狂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.22,0:00:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是讓我成為創造新人類的神？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.33,0:00:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是神！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.82,0:00:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要成為 為人類照亮未來的光明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.05,0:00:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光明？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.42,0:00:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是高達？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.37,0:00:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是EXA-DB孕育了它
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它就是人類歷史錯誤的象徵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.18,0:00:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要擊敗它 繼承伊澤爾坎特大人的意志！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.07,0:02:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏附近就有EXA-DB…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.97,0:03:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能駕馭它
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.72,0:03:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Legilis！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.30,0:03:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希德… 原來是真實存在的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希德？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.61,0:03:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EXA-DB的守護者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.48,0:03:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有自我防禦技能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.46,0:03:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那種無人機動戰士的代號
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用EXA-DB的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.62,0:03:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像生物一樣不斷進化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.75,0:03:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正所謂怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.92,0:03:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它擁有的力量 無人可以想像
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.01,0:03:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特大人請回來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.01,0:03:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台機動戰士太危險
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.82,0:03:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是高達Legilis 您隻身一人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.01,0:03:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 它必須由我擊敗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我命中注定的試煉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.69,0:04:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不能在這裏取勝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就沒有繼承伊澤爾坎特大人意志的資格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.63,0:04:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼承伊澤爾坎特大人的…意志
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.14,0:04:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著吧 什麼是高達真正的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須做到和伊澤爾坎特大人那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.82,0:04:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者更高一層的覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則無法發揮這台高達的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.11,0:04:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我言出必行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這台高達Legilis
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.92,0:04:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將勝利掌握在手中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:04:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索敵系統報告
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.24,0:05:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監測到機動戰士反應
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.06,0:05:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是資源開發小行星聚集的軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.26,0:05:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 沒有情報顯示周圍有友軍出戰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 為防萬一確認…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.72,0:05:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒有這個必要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的第一要務是前往諾德拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.06,0:05:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行攻略拉·格拉密斯要塞的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.16,0:05:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒空沿途沾花惹草
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.02,0:05:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.98,0:05:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續監視 有情況匯報
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.08,0:05:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.34,0:05:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確定嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.97,0:05:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.10,0:05:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代號希德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.79,0:05:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,13年前 讓你身負重傷的怪物又露面了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希德
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全看不清楚敵人的相貌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這傢伙襲擊的艦船嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.75,0:06:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是B班 請求支援
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快來 這樣下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 明明只是調查一艘漂流船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.86,0:07:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友軍機？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑弗裏 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希德出現 證明EXA-DB就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.73,0:07:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會在這個節骨眼上遇到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥準備
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.27,0:07:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要親手摧毀EXA-DB
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.78,0:07:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必通知天神號嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.85,0:08:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不只是戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.01,0:08:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是清剿威脅地球的惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.60,0:08:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人必須一個不留全部殺光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親為了復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會將EXA-DB用於這場戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.02,0:08:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那樣和維甘沒有區別
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.63,0:08:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只會使軍事力量的平衡遭到破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.21,0:08:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.91,0:08:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓如今的聯邦得到EXA-DB太過危險
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.91,0:08:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我們暗中銷毀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.33,0:08:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真會找罪受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.96,0:08:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對它的能耐 我有切身體會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次不會搞砸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.89,0:08:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴洛諾克 改變軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.62,0:08:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？我可沒收到他們的聯絡…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.69,0:08:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是打算去發生戰鬥的宇域嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.32,0:09:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的我行我素不是第一天了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.66,0:09:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.35,0:09:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐 把適配器遞給我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.83,0:09:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.72,0:09:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人叫你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.89,0:09:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.80,0:09:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這兒有點事 你們先走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.68,0:09:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.06,0:09:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要和我們一起參加戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.14,0:09:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會追上你們的 別這副表情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.30,0:09:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放任老人家自己去 不知會幹出什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒這能耐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.13,0:09:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺根本不聽我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.95,0:09:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的想法不可能輕易被改變
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.60,0:09:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但真誠的交流絕不會白費
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別急著放棄 吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.84,0:10:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺他一定明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.81,0:10:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.48,0:10:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變軌完成 鎖定目標坐標
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.78,0:10:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.09,0:10:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴洛諾克 全速航行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.40,0:10:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找那隻怪物算賬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都給我打起精神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.59,0:10:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.78,0:10:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到接近它會如此困難
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:10:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甄選出值得生存下去的種群
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.11,0:11:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓人活得更有尊嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.17,0:11:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸計劃將為我們打開通往新世界的大門
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.25,0:11:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也可以把它理解成創造新的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.68,0:11:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知自己的所作所為 會造成怎樣的犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.02,0:11:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意聽好 地球種們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.83,0:11:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維甘在此 宣佈開始全面侵略地球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊澤爾坎特大人全心為人類的未來著想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.39,0:11:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥到了今天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是否願意陪我的瘋狂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.76,0:11:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.39,0:12:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誓將人類 帶往伊甸！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.19,0:12:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.10,0:12:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正逐漸發揮出Legilis的全部性能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.52,0:13:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種距離下的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.04,0:13:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.94,0:13:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.70,0:13:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…難道是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.66,0:13:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下方？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.54,0:13:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱身斗篷？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.16,0:13:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機動戰士竟然也有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.23,0:13:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那原本就是來自EXA-DB的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.76,0:13:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希德在成長過程中擁有 也不足為奇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這塊不算廣闊的宇域裏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EXA-DB可以隱匿至今
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.82,0:13:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來和那種能力有密切關係
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.37,0:13:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.76,0:13:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在出去也只會礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fon·Farsia的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.02,0:14:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少可以成為傑哈特大人的盾牌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瞭解傑哈特大人的為人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.04,0:14:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不可能允許你這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.02,0:14:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要相信傑哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥宇域附近發現反應
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.25,0:14:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是機動戰士！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.77,0:14:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.10,0:14:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會錯 是希德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.22,0:14:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.33,0:14:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們去找出EXA-DB
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.48,0:14:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.52,0:14:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.33,0:14:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在火星上遇到過的維甘高達！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.05,0:15:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別來礙事 亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.26,0:15:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.16,0:15:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我自己的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.95,0:15:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是在考驗我作為伊澤爾坎特大人繼承者的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.54,0:15:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勸你別來插手 盡快離開這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.62,0:15:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊澤爾坎特的繼承者？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.28,0:15:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特 你這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.08,0:15:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.01,0:15:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和這東西有交戰經驗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.03,0:15:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少還記得它的行動規律
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來吸引它 快逃 傑哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.79,0:15:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還在說這種話！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.63,0:15:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.23,0:16:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全無影無蹤了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.50,0:16:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船…船長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.11,0:16:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.66,0:16:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的行動…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.16,0:16:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了 那顆小行星裏藏著EXA-DB
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.12,0:17:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.22,0:17:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣永遠無法捉住它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.87,0:17:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如一試
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.47,0:17:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆 想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.06,0:17:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錨索發射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.27,0:17:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 看你往哪兒跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.51,0:17:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.04,0:17:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它就在纜繩的末端
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.21,0:17:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中攻擊那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.81,0:17:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纜繩？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.36,0:17:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.33,0:18:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.14,0:18:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我掌握了！高達Legilis的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.41,0:18:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.85,0:19:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於成功駕馭了高達Legilis
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了 被詛咒的秘寶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.13,0:19:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是EXA-DB嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:19:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你摧毀它
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.05,0:20:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我讓開 亞瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.13,0:20:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 EXA-DB不能留在世上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.00,0:20:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EXA-DB對我軍來說是必不可少的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.68,0:20:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒看見它造出怎樣的怪物嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.16,0:20:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實 EXA-DB的力量是被詛咒的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.25,0:20:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我有能力控制那樣的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.22,0:20:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是為了人類的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.62,0:20:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.15,0:21:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命中目標
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在確認EXA-DB是否完全被摧毀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.84,0:21:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是你說要打的 船長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.76,0:21:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會有事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.79,0:21:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.75,0:21:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EXA-DB…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.92,0:21:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去它或許令人惋惜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.63,0:21:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我得到了高達Legilis的全部能力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.11,0:22:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊澤爾坎特大人的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.03,0:22:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經繼承了它
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.81,0:24:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰士們帶著各自的思緒和覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.33,0:24:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踏上決戰的戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.76,0:24:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 機動戰士高達AGE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.46,0:24:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙要塞 拉·格拉密斯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.67,0:24:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個人的命運成就歷史

